install schematic cli

- npm install -g @angular-devkit/schematics-cli
- schematics blank --name= schematics-name
- cd ./schematics-name
    - npm run build
    - npm link <path_to_Schematic>/schematic-name

add watch mode 
- "watch": "tsc -p tsconfig.json --watch",

followed this link and basic schematics is working
- https://dev.to/shhdharmen/different-ways-to-run-schematics-from-another-schematics-1jd1
